              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "For each  event the measured proton momentum was used",
                " to calculate the expected kinematical quantities  of",
                " the  deuteron.  By  comparing  these to the measured",
                " values    a    clean    separation    of    two-body",
                " photodisintegration from background was achieved."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrections had to be applied to the data for: - loss",
                " of particles due to nuclear interactions",
                " (9 to 26%, depending on particle energy);",
                " - uncorrelated background events (2%  for low photon",
                "   energies and forward angles,  going up to 26%  for",
                "   m0  the highest photon energies and extreme proton",
                "   backward angle);",
                " - a false determination of the g-quanta energy (this",
                "   error  is  biggest for the steepest slope in cross",
                "   section versus energy and is estimated to be  less",
                "   than 15%)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " statistical errors."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Systematic errors  due  to  uncertainties  in",
                " target thickness were estimated as 1%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Systematic errors due to uncertainties in the",
                " solid angle were estimated as 2%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The He-3(g,p)d  reaction has been investigated in the",
                " photon energy region between 200 MeV and 450 MeV  at",
                " a  proton  c.m.  angles  between 20 and 150 degrees.",
                " Protons and deuterons were detected  in  coincidence",
                " with  two time-of-flight spectrometers consisting of",
                " scintillation   counters;   both   particles    were",
                " identified   and  their  energies  and  angles  were",
                " measured.  The angular distributions show  a  strong",
                " forward  peak.  The differential cross sections fall",
                " off with increasing photon energy without showing  a",
                " significant influence of the delta-resonance."
              ]
            }
          ],
